{"TopicId":136557,"ForumId":44,"TopicTitle":"Most Humanlike robot EVER! *Insert extra clickbait here*","CreatedByName":"daniel l.","CreatedById":57763,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-09T21:44:55Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"daniel l.","CreatedById":57763,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-09T21:44:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://singularityhub.com/2016/03/29/human-like-robot-interviewed-at-sxsw-its-here-to-help-and-destroy-video/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://singularityhub.com/2016/03/29/human-like-robot-interviewed-at-sxsw-its-here-to-help-and-destroy-video/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/W0_DPi0PmF0?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh my gosh.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-09T22:20:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, it\u0027s a T-600?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YumonStudios","CreatedById":161509,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-10T03:14:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222505230\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136557\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460238295\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257763\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022daniel l.\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 hours ago, daniel l. said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://singularityhub.com/2016/03/29/human-like-robot-interviewed-at-sxsw-its-here-to-help-and-destroy-video/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://singularityhub.com/2016/03/29/human-like-robot-interviewed-at-sxsw-its-here-to-help-and-destroy-video/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/W0_DPi0PmF0?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh my gosh.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe\u0027ve reached the uncanny valley.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think non-humanlike robots will become more popular (or at least resemble humans, but a lot less than this) simply due to that. She is creepy.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt also raises the question of robot ethics and control of the technology.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"daniel l.","CreatedById":57763,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-10T03:16:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222505596\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136557\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460258072\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161509\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022YumonStudios\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 hours ago, YumonStudios said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe\u0027ve reached the uncanny valley.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think non-humanlike robots will become more popular (or at least resemble humans, but a lot less than this) simply due to that. She is creepy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt also raises the question of robot ethics and control of the technology.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe problem i saw was that her eyes didnt move, They stayed staring in one direction the whole time, The eyes need to focus on things around her, Especially things that would catch the eye of a human, The eyes should also have a slight random twitch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YumonStudios","CreatedById":161509,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-10T03:23:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222505602\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136557\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460258218\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257763\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022daniel l.\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, daniel l. said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe problem i saw was that her eyes didnt move, They stayed staring in one direction the whole time, The eyes need to focus on things around her, Especially things that would catch the eye of a human, The eyes should also have a slight random twitch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0I have a feeling that if human robots become a thing, they\u0027ll be made cartoonish and obviously not human, just to bypass the uncanny valley.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m looking forward to my IRL MegaMan. Hey, if Capcom won\u0027t make any games for it...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-10T03:23:29Z\u0022 title=\u002204/10/2016 03:23  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 10, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by YumonStudios\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-10T12:37:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow they \u003Cs\u003Eshould\u003C/s\u003E must combine it with \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rVlhMGQgDkY\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EBoston Dynamics\u0027 Atlas\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0 and \u003Ca href=\u0022http://fortune.com/2016/03/30/microsofts-tay-return/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EMicrosoft\u0027s Tay\u003C/a\u003E. Then teach some \u003Ca href=\u0022https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/1/17/Terminatrix1001.jpg\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ekung fu\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nibb31","CreatedById":7272,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-10T18:34:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nToo creepy to be of any use.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RainDreamer","CreatedById":129077,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-11T08:57:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have a feeling this thing will hunt down human to rip their faces off and wears that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"magnemoe","CreatedById":57801,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-11T11:22:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222505613\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136557\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460258598\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161509\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022YumonStudios\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10.4.2016 at 5:23 AM, YumonStudios said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0I have a feeling that if human robots become a thing, they\u0027ll be made cartoonish and obviously not human, just to bypass the uncanny valley.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m looking forward to my IRL MegaMan. Hey, if Capcom won\u0027t make any games for it...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is an simple solution for all sort of service robots you will interact with, you know its an robot so why try to hide it, on the other hand having it showing emotions is an benefit then interacting.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bill Phil","CreatedById":127797,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-11T12:39:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222507706\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136557\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460373723\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257801\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022magnemoe\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, magnemoe said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is an simple solution for all sort of service robots you will interact with, you know its an robot so why try to hide it, on the other hand having it showing emotions is an benefit then interacting.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s easier to animate emotions than physically show them. Moon did it that way.... And it wasn\u0027t creepy. It was just smiley faces and variations of those.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AngelLestat","CreatedById":58968,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-11T14:02:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey spend so much in that and they could not get a\u00A0wig?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}